<plot>The plot of Song emerges from the mouth of a small boy as if he is singing his own future. The story leaps forward to a time when the singer, now a young thug, is in a rundown karaoke bar, apparently waiting for some sort of violent showdown. A timid university student enters the bar, coerced by his bossy girlfriend, and is confronted by the thug with hair raising results.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?506686</url></doc>
